ProfileName: Valerie J. Wood "Author and Sports Journalist"
Summary: Adult Pups seem to really like this one
text: Always looking for a few alternatives for dry food. I don't like feeding the same brand constantly and this has become a great alternate with the other quality dry foods we give our big pups. Quality ingredients are important. As long as your dog doesn't need to be on a special diet, you can alternate quality foods for them. They like this one. Would definitely recommend it.
